name: 4ft x 3ft Vinyl Photography Backdrop / Cherry Tree Row / Custom Photo Prop
description:
Listing is for:
*4ft x 3ft Cherry Tree Row

~OUR PRODUCT~
We strive to have the highest quality vinyl backdrops at the absolute lowest price.
Our backdrops are printed using the latest (state of the art) technology. The artwork is very high quality, so it can scale properly. Our vinyl backdrops are waterproof, glare free and roll out flat.

~HANGING OUR BACKDROPS~
Typically Photographers(including myself) use photography backdrop clamps to hang these on a stand. However, we can add Grommets or Pole pockets for a small additional charge(Please request this before ordering).

~CUSTOM ORDERS~
Not seeing something your looking for? Or want this in a different size? Just message us and we will see what we have. We can also have any image you have printed as long as you have the copyrights and the image is large enough. We do charge a small $5 charge for custom orders.

~CARE & CLEANING~
Our vinyl backdrops are prefect for birthday smash cake pictures and newborns, So don't worry about the messes. Just take a damp cloth with water and/or a gentle cleaner(like soap) and wipe clean. In some cases the backdrops could become wrinkled, just lay them face side down for 24 hours or so and they should become flat again. You could also lay it flat, face down in outside in the heat to remove creases.

~SHIPPING~
Our turn around time for US is approx 1-2 weeks for printing and shipping. We have had buyers receive their items as early as 2 days! There may be rare cases in which this may take a little longer. WE CAN RUSH ORDERS FOR AN ADDITIONAL CHARGE. Please contact me for details.

~INTERNATIONAL SHIPPING~
We ship almost ANYWHERE. If an item doesn't have the option to ship to your country, please contact me and I can add it. Shipping time for international will vary.

If you have any additional questions please feel free to ask. We are available to answer questions 7 days a week.

name: 10 Ft Telescopic Background Backdrop Support Stand Crossbar System Photo Studio
description:
Perfect for any backdrop......

10' x 6-1/5' Professional Telescopic Photo Backdrop Support Stand Kit!

This brand new portable background/backdrop support stand kit is extremely suitable for all level photographers from amateurs to professionals. It is a perfect solution to produce photo and video for web retailers and commercial product catalog, especially for costume and portrait. Very easy to use and set up in minutes.

Best Solution for Your Professional Photo Studio:

    Strong support capacity but lightweight.
    Assembly frames for suitable background of different size objects.
    Fit for both fabric (canvas/ muslin) and paper backgrounds.
    Perfect for costume, portrait and large object photography.
    Set up in minutes and stored in portable carrying case.

Telescopic Background/Backdrop Support Stand:

    Strong alloy steel construction.
    6-1/5 ft Max. fully extended height and 2-2/5 ft Min. height.
    Supports background up to 10 ft width.
    Two-section separate telescopic crossbars can adjust width from 5-2/5 ft to 10 ft easily.
    Extra wide footprint with rubber tips for more stability.
    Simple press-to-lock locks provide fast precise height adjustment.
    Folding frame design for freewill lighting position setting and easier storage. 

Carrying Case:

This listing is for all three backdrop, floordrop and baseboard in one!!! Total size is 48" x 99".

~OUR PRODUCT~
We strive to have the highest quality vinyl backdrops at the absolute lowest price.
Our backdrops are printed using the latest (state of the art) technology. The artwork is very high quality, so it can scale properly. Our vinyl backdrops are waterproof, glare free and roll out flat.

~HANGING OUR BACKDROPS~
Typically Photographers(including myself) use photography backdrop clamps to hang these on a stand. However, we can add Grommets or Pole pockets for a small additional charge(Please request this before ordering).

~CUSTOM ORDERS~ 
Not seeing something your looking for? Or want this in a different size? Just message us and we will see what we have. We can also have any image you have printed as long as you have the copyrights and the image is large enough. We do charge a small $5 charge for custom orders. 

~CARE & CLEANING~
Our vinyl backdrops are prefect for birthday smash cake pictures and newborns, So don't worry about the messes. Just take a damp cloth with water and/or a gentle cleaner(like soap) and wipe clean. In some cases the backdrops could become wrinkled, just lay them face side down for 24 hours or so and they should become flat again. You could also lay it flat, face down in outside in the heat to remove creases. 

~SHIPPING~
Our turn around time for US is approx 1-2 weeks for printing and shipping. We have had buyers receive their items as early as 2 days! There may be rare cases in which this may take a little longer. WE CAN RUSH ORDERS FOR AN ADDITIONAL CHARGE. Please contact me for details.

~INTERNATIONAL SHIPPING~ 
We ship almost ANYWHERE. If an item doesn't have the option to ship to your country, please contact me and I can add it. Shipping time for international will vary.
